{"type": "article", "id": 10138, "title": "伐开心，看看这些世界上最悲伤的logo们", "description": "世界那么大，logo 们也想静静。", "date": "2015-05-28T14:41:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}], "category": 18, "author": 112316, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 186, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021221124Ws3BeJ9pEgo5Dj1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t有人把耐克的 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">slogan </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Just Do It</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”画成了“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Just Do Not</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”发布在推特上引发众人围观。</span><p></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122108az497CSnpVXYILtE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这位插画家名叫库尔茨（<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Adam J. Kurtz</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">），</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在玩坏了耐克的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">之后，他在几个小时之内又陆续发出了其他品牌 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的悲伤时刻，你会看见可口可乐、星巴克等众多 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一起组成“世界上最悲伤的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">们”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t“真诚是人们最为立体有趣的情感，把一些悲伤的元素加入品牌 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中或许会很有意思”，库尔茨对 </span><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/\">Adweek</a> 表示。作为 <a href=\"http://yrbff.tumblr.com/\">BuzzFeed <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公司 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">BFF</span></a> 创意团队的一员，他热爱新颖有趣的创意。在他看来，品牌 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">logo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不应该是大众在社交平台上秀日常的一个“植入”，尽管人们在社交平台中光鲜亮丽，但更多时候心里是有一些负能量的，现在他希望用一种更为幽默的方式表达出来。</span><p></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t他还在<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ADAMJK\">推特</a>上说，如果同时有两件耐克的 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">T </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">恤摆在他的面前，一件写着“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Just Do It</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”，一件写着“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Just Do Not</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”，他会选择后者。</span><p></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">下面我们来看看这些 logo：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122108XIJPBTskdV1ngvir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">百加得（<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">BACARDI</span>）：变成了“</span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">BACARDOT”。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122109zejxwK7oBrs59MvX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;text-indent:28px;white-space:normal;\">露诗 (LUSH)：我</span>快要尖叫出来了，你能听见我的声音吗？<br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122109efU46P0SokByGmgr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">企鹅：救救我，为了保持我 1935 年来的领导地位，我脖子都抽筋了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122109WgdHCfSapukvToK8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t可口可乐：喝了这饮料，所有的破事都来了。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122110Jxpy9glXwhuk4iGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">蓝带</span><span style=\"color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">啤酒</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">(Pabst Blue Ribbon)：噢</span>，然而它还只是一杯啤酒。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122110R0AezxpqTIwHNUQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">Chipotle </span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;\">快餐店：难吃到死。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122111XTGqp87gfRsQtiUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t星巴克：不许拍照。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122111NizS3RJfwFPHqI4Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t宜家：<span style=\"color:#3F3F3F;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">家具特么要你自己装！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t特别说明：非官方翻译，各位请随意\r\n</p>\n\n"}